title: /C O R R E C T I O N -- Cadence Design Systems, Inc./
text:
Cadence Design Systems, Inc. 
In the news release, Cadence Announces Third Quarter 2015 Financial Results Webcast, issued 09-Oct-2015 by Cadence Design Systems, Inc. over PR Newswire, we are advised by the company that CFO Commentary has been added to the release. The complete, corrected release follows: 
Cadence Announces Third Quarter 2015 Financial Results Webcast 
SAN JOSE, Calif., Oct. 9, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- 
WHO: Cadence Design Systems, Inc. (NASDAQ: CDNS) to announce third quarter 2015 financial results via webcast. 
WHAT: You are invited to attend the third quarter 2015 financial results audio webcast. Participating on the webcast will be Lip-Bu Tan, president and chief executive officer, and Geoff Ribar, senior vice president and chief financial officer. 
WHEN: The webcast will begin Monday, Oct. 26, 2015 at 2:00 p.m. (Pacific) / 5:00 p.m. (Eastern). An archive of the webcast will be available from 5:00 p.m. (Pacific) on Oct. 26, 2015 until 5:00 p.m. (Pacific) on Dec. 18, 2015. 
WHERE: The webcast will be available online at: www.cadence.com/cadence/investor_relations 
CFO COMMENTARY: Cadence will provide a written commentary on its third quarter 2015 financial results from Geoff Ribar, senior vice president and chief financial officer. The commentary will be posted to the Cadence Investor Relations website ( www.cadence.com/cadence/investor_relations ) after the third quarter 2015 financial results are publicly disclosed. 
For more information, please contact: Therese Papenfuss
